| 11th  | +4 | Nomadic Tradition feature |   7    |   4   |   3   |   3   |   —   |   —   |
| 12th  | +4 | Ability Score Improvement, Martial Versatility     |   7    |   4   |   3   |   3   |   —   |   —   |
