**Psi Cost:** :: 1 psi point
**Manifesting Time:** :: 1 bonus action
**Range:** :: Self
**Components:** :: O
**Duration:** :: 1 turn
You channel your potential for violence into one strike. If the next melee weapon attack you make after manifesting this power hits, the attack deals an additional 1d10 damage of that attack's damage type. If your attack deals more than one type of damage, you choose which type. If the next attack you make after manifesting this power misses, the power ends with no effect.

***Intensify.*** When you spend extra psi points to manifest this augment, the additional damage increases by 1d10 for each additional psi point spent beyond the minimum cost.

