## Vitality Transfer Field
*5th-level psychometabolism*
**Augmenting:** ::*autonomous vitality*
**Psi Cost:** ::9 psi points
**Manifesting Time:** ::1 action
**Range:** ::Self (60-foot radius)
**Components:** ::O
**Duration:** ::Instantaneous

You generate a field of sympathetic transference of life energy.

Choose up to six creatures within range. Each target regains hit points equal to 15 + your psionic ability modifier, and you take 1d4 necrotic damage for each creature healed this way. The damage you take cannot be mitigated in any way.

***Intensify.*** When you spend extra psi points to manifest this augment, for each additional psi point spent beyond the minimum cost the amount of hit points every target creature regains increases by 5 and the total damage you take increases by 1d4.


